{"tid":1196661,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚抬我出去果幾位義士，好多謝你哋","createTime":"2019-06-09T22:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T08:19:17.000Z","uid":120631,"like":110,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eb9b0c680b3cbf081345265aa9c8914de15cf9b5","tid":1196661,"uid":120631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T22:20:06.000Z","msg":"夜晚喺立法會出面幫手搬鐵馬嗰時<br />\n我一放低就畀黑警噴撚到成身都係胡椒噴霧<br />\n我對眼同手腳都中到應一應<br />\n即刻睇唔到嘢兼仆咗落啲鐵馬到<br />\n好好彩有幾位義士即刻抬咗我出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫我處理我皮膚上嘅痛<br />\n雖然我睇唔到你哋咩樣，但好想多謝你哋<br />\n如果無你哋幫我一定畀人拉鳩走<br />\n<br />\n仲有喺公廁出面幾位黑衫朋友仔<br />\n陪咗我好耐又幫我沖水又盛<br />\n有啲行過嘅人都不斷問我使唔使幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真心想講聲多謝<br />\n同埋尊重所有出過嚟同願意留守甚至衝過嘅人<br />\n多謝你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606faa5f758d3a774f9821bf2eea53f0a5b71ea6","tid":1196661,"uid":194177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T22:22:07.000Z","msg":"鍵盤戰士都有價值 整理咗戰線幫手做文宣！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/cKvbAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/cKvbAS</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1b203bbbd0ab2a85b4477a9ce835dd8cf03e300b","tid":1196661,"uid":184094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T22:29:08.000Z","msg":"紅衫？"},{"pid":"4b5a504ced8d553229b7511adb12b9b7b2437e16","tid":1196661,"uid":120631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b203bbbd0ab2a85b4477a9ce835dd8cf03e300b","tid":1196661,"uid":184094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T22:29:08.000Z","msg":"紅衫？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T22:35:43.000Z","msg":"唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b6f6508af40103a80a5014fc6a930d8a4738c7","tid":1196661,"uid":115714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b5a504ced8d553229b7511adb12b9b7b2437e16","tid":1196661,"uid":120631,"like":0,"dislike":